  "description": "Every capability active simultaneously: FM (0.42) + Drift Bus (journeyMode=1.0, driftDepth=0.75) + all 3 FX (delay+chorus+reverb) + all 4 mods + 3 active processors. Wavetable (Harmonic) as FM modulator for Saw carrier. proc1=LP (formant whisper), proc2=Wavefold (harmonic complexity), proc3=BP (selective resonance at 1100 Hz). The Four Mods: LFO→wtPos (wavetable morphing), LFO→pan (coprime sweep), Env→cutoff1 (filter breathes with notes), Aftertouch→amp (living dynamic response). This is the full OBRIX organism — all systems active, the reef at full metabolic capacity.",
